# Project Structure

## Root Directories

- [app/](mdc:app/) - Next.js App Router (dashboard, appointments, auth)
- [components/](mdc:components/) - React components by domain
- [lib/](mdc:lib/) - Utilities, config, business logic
- [services/](mdc:services/) - API services and business logic
- [types/](mdc:types/) - TypeScript type definitions
- [store/](mdc:store/) - State management (Zustand)
- [hooks/](mdc:hooks/) - Custom React hooks
- [utils/](mdc:utils/) - Utility functions

## App Routes

- `app/(public)/` - Non-authenticated
- `app/auth/` - Login, register, forgot-password
- `app/appointments/` - Patient appointments
- `app/dashboard/` - Provider dashboard
  - `appointments/`, `doctors/`, `patients/`, `services/`, `drugs/`, `users/`, `organizations/`, `emails/`, `newsletters/`
- `app/profile/` - User profile
- `app/s/[subdomain]/` - Multi-tenant

## Components

- `components/client/appointments/` - Patient-facing
- `components/dashboard/` - Provider dashboard
- `components/auth/` - Authentication
- `components/ui/` - Reusable UI
- `components/sections/` - Page sections
- `components/layouts/` - Layouts

## Services

- `services/client/` - appointment, doctor, patient, drug, email, newsletters, service
- `services/common/` - auth, user, activity, notifications
- `services/system/` - organization
- `services/external/` - Third-party integrations

## Key Config Files

- [lib/config.ts](mdc:lib/config.ts) - App settings (timings, clinic info)
- [lib/auth.ts](mdc:lib/auth.ts), [lib/serverAuth.ts](mdc:lib/serverAuth.ts) - Authentication
- [lib/validation.ts](mdc:lib/validation.ts) - Validation schemas
- [lib/interface.ts](mdc:lib/interface.ts) - TypeScript interfaces
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Design system
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript config
